1
00:00:14,575 --> 00:00:20,013
<i>Connecting old words</i>
<i>that have been used up</i>

2
00:00:20,848 --> 00:00:28,755
<i>I just want to convey</i>
<i>my simple thoughts</i>

3
00:00:28,823 --> 00:00:34,193
<i>That day's faint wind blows away</i>

4
00:00:34,261 --> 00:00:38,322
<i>at the castle ruins of yesterday</i>

5
00:00:39,567 --> 00:00:44,470
<i>I'll laugh with you</i>
<i>and live for the moment</i>

6
00:00:45,206 --> 00:00:52,112
<i>Still that incident</i>
<i>will continue to trouble you, right?</i>

7
00:00:53,514 --> 00:00:57,006
<i>That's why it must be good bye</i>

8
00:00:57,084 --> 00:01:04,047
<i>Leaving nothing behind,</i>
<i>let us share what is left</i>

9
00:01:04,125 --> 00:01:11,190
<i>In time, we'll realize</i>
<i>that it was everything</i>

10
00:01:11,265 --> 00:01:17,932
<i>And sadness will touch our cheeks,</i>
<i>creating a river of tears</i>

11
00:01:18,406 --> 00:01:27,906
<i>Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex</i>
<i>and melting away</i>

12
00:01:43,908 --> 00:01:47,935
But thank goodness
your injury wasn't serious.

13
00:01:49,847 --> 00:01:51,508
Naruto was relieved, too...

14
00:02:07,031 --> 00:02:08,965
<i>The rumors were true...</i>

15
00:02:09,534 --> 00:02:12,697
<i>That the survivor of the Village's</i>
<i>honorable Uchiha Clan</i>

16
00:02:12,770 --> 00:02:15,170
<i>was the most good for nothing kid...</i>

17
00:02:22,847 --> 00:02:27,181
Sasuke, you must be hungry.
Is there something you want to eat?

18
00:02:27,719 --> 00:02:29,482
I'll go buy something for you.

19
00:02:37,028 --> 00:02:41,465
<i>The Battle Begins.</i>
<i>Naruto vs. Sasuke</i>

20
00:02:43,468 --> 00:02:46,164
To be honest,
I really don't understand.

21
00:02:46,938 --> 00:02:49,634
It seems there were opinions that,

22
00:02:49,707 --> 00:02:51,971
with the final exam being suspended,

23
00:02:52,043 --> 00:02:55,979
no one should pass
this time around.

24
00:02:56,648 --> 00:03:02,018
But I hear the late Third Hokage
highly praised your match.

25
00:03:03,087 --> 00:03:05,521
It seems he intended to recommend you
for Chunin.

26
00:03:06,824 --> 00:03:09,156
The lords of other lands
who observed the fight

27
00:03:09,227 --> 00:03:11,457
and the proctors were of
the same opinion as well...

28
00:03:12,363 --> 00:03:15,491
In that case, it's not in my place
to say this or that about it.

29
00:03:16,367 --> 00:03:17,299
From now on,

30
00:03:17,368 --> 00:03:20,735
strive to perform in a manner
that is worthy of that headband...

31
00:03:21,372 --> 00:03:24,864
Congratulations!
As of today, you're a Chunin!

32
00:03:27,311 --> 00:03:29,245
- Wow...
- Wow!

33
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:33,712
Even you who's never motivated
look respectable.

34
00:03:34,919 --> 00:03:36,113
It doesn't suit you.

35
00:03:37,321 --> 00:03:38,447
Don't laugh, I say...

36
00:03:39,157 --> 00:03:40,317
For the time being

37
00:03:40,391 --> 00:03:43,827
let's have a toast to celebrate
Shikamaru's promotion to Chunin!

38
00:03:44,662 --> 00:03:46,061
Let's eat!

39
00:03:46,864 --> 00:03:48,229
Oh! Choji!

40
00:03:48,299 --> 00:03:50,995
Don't eat the meat before the toast!

41
00:03:51,335 --> 00:03:54,498
But, it'd be a waste if it got burned, so...

42
00:03:54,706 --> 00:03:57,072
There's a lot of meat. Eat up!

43
00:03:57,175 --> 00:03:58,506
All right!

44
00:04:46,657 --> 00:04:49,922
<i>Right now,</i>
<i>I have no interest in you...</i>

45
00:04:51,896 --> 00:04:54,091
<i>Your target is Naruto, after all.</i>

46
00:05:07,278 --> 00:05:09,678
You'll end up in the hospital again, Choji.

47
00:05:09,747 --> 00:05:12,238
Don't you know how to savor the taste?

48
00:05:12,717 --> 00:05:13,684
Never mind!

49
00:05:13,818 --> 00:05:17,379
Even if I eat a lot,
I know how to savor properly.

50
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:26,259
Hey! Choji, that's the last piece of meat
that I've been grilling

51
00:05:26,564 --> 00:05:27,929
The last bite!

52
00:05:27,999 --> 00:05:29,591
This is the conclusion and

53
00:05:29,667 --> 00:05:33,125
will become the meat with
the greatest value that should be savored!

54
00:05:33,738 --> 00:05:38,072
I won't hand over
this last bite to anyone!

55
00:05:39,944 --> 00:05:43,311
What're you acting cool for,
you idiot?!

56
00:05:43,381 --> 00:05:46,942
Everyone makes fun of you
because you're like this!

57
00:05:47,251 --> 00:05:48,775
- You're just a fat
- Ino!

58
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:50,685
That's a taboo word!

59
00:05:50,988 --> 00:05:52,421
But really, Choji...

60
00:05:52,890 --> 00:05:54,721
A meal isn't a battle.

61
00:05:54,959 --> 00:05:57,860
Relax at a time like this at least.
What a pain.

62
00:06:03,134 --> 00:06:07,264
<i>Vulgar... Dirty mouthed...</i>
<i>Too lazy...</i>

63
00:06:08,005 --> 00:06:10,530
<i>I wonder if these guys</i>
<i>will be okay from here.</i>

64
00:06:11,342 --> 00:06:12,206
<i>In particular...</i>

65
00:06:12,844 --> 00:06:15,574
Choji. With you it's nothing but food.

66
00:06:16,347 --> 00:06:17,712
Do a little training sometime!

67
00:06:35,466 --> 00:06:36,558
Choji...

68
00:06:36,901 --> 00:06:40,962
You're lucky that your mind
doesn't restrict what you eat...

69
00:06:41,639 --> 00:06:44,039
I've got it rough with a diet.

70
00:06:44,275 --> 00:06:46,266
Why do you have to diet, Ino?

71
00:06:46,644 --> 00:06:52,412
Girls want to be seen as cute as possible
by the one they like!

72
00:06:55,119 --> 00:06:58,748
But that person might not always
like a thin person.

73
00:06:59,457 --> 00:07:01,687
In the first place,
most boys don't like fat

74
00:07:01,759 --> 00:07:04,922
Not that... They like thin girls.

75
00:07:05,529 --> 00:07:08,191
And, vice versa.

76
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:15,805
You should be a little more conscious
of your body, Choji.

77
00:07:15,973 --> 00:07:18,100
You won't be popular.

78
00:07:21,245 --> 00:07:23,270
Heh... She doesn't get it.

79
00:07:23,748 --> 00:07:28,412
Men don't like thin women
as much as women think.

80
00:07:28,686 --> 00:07:33,988
More likely men who like chubby women
are the most common.

81
00:07:34,792 --> 00:07:37,989
And, vice versa... I'd say.

82
00:07:38,863 --> 00:07:40,626
I bet she'd be twice as popular

83
00:07:40,698 --> 00:07:44,634
if she were to gain a little more weight
instead of dieting.

84
00:07:49,073 --> 00:07:51,598
You sure are a funny guy, Shikamaru.

85
00:07:51,676 --> 00:07:53,371
And you're smart, too.

86
00:07:53,444 --> 00:07:53,933
Hmm?

87
00:07:54,345 --> 00:07:55,937
I know it in my heart...

88
00:07:56,414 --> 00:08:01,044
You're much more awesome
than the likes of Sasuke or Neji.

89
00:08:03,688 --> 00:08:09,388
Well, I've never even thought about that.
I'm me, so...

90
00:08:09,961 --> 00:08:12,589
But you're the only one
who became a Chunin

91
00:08:12,663 --> 00:08:14,961
in the Chunin Exam this time...

92
00:08:15,733 --> 00:08:19,601
But you might be better
at fighting, right?

93
00:08:20,438 --> 00:08:23,601
I might've given up if
I'd gotten into one with you.

94
00:08:24,342 --> 00:08:27,311
But earlier,
Sensei told me that all I do is eat

95
00:08:27,378 --> 00:08:28,845
and that I'm not progressing...

96
00:08:28,913 --> 00:08:33,043
I'm me, I tell you. And you're you.

97
00:08:33,384 --> 00:08:36,512
It's stupid talking about how which is.

98
00:08:38,856 --> 00:08:42,656
Well, don't worry too much
about what Asuma says...

99
00:08:43,094 --> 00:08:46,257
You should live naturally
and take things easy.

100
00:08:48,165 --> 00:08:49,962
See you later! I'm going home.

101
00:08:50,501 --> 00:08:52,935
My dad's starting to say
some troublesome thing

102
00:08:53,004 --> 00:08:55,768
like he's going to teach me
a new Jutsu or something.

103
00:08:56,140 --> 00:08:57,164
Shikamaru.

104
00:08:58,109 --> 00:08:58,973
Hmm?

105
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:03,676
What?

106
00:09:05,149 --> 00:09:06,776
Good luck with your training.

107
00:09:10,955 --> 00:09:11,785
Yeah.

108
00:09:12,990 --> 00:09:15,686
<i>You're a good guy...Choji.</i>

109
00:09:34,478 --> 00:09:36,002
Hey, Sakura!

110
00:09:39,583 --> 00:09:40,379
<i>Naruto!</i>

111
00:09:47,558 --> 00:09:48,820
The time is right...

112
00:09:50,594 --> 00:09:53,154
Head for the Leaf Village, now!

113
00:09:57,574 --> 00:09:59,974
I see... You've made up your mind, huh?

114
00:10:00,210 --> 00:10:00,904
Yes!

115
00:10:00,977 --> 00:10:04,071
I'm carrying out fitness training
to get ready for the surgery.

116
00:10:04,647 --> 00:10:07,343
I want to return as soon as
I can after the surgery, so...

117
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:10,945
Oww!

118
00:10:11,121 --> 00:10:12,588
Ow ow...

119
00:10:19,829 --> 00:10:20,488
Lee...

120
00:10:20,797 --> 00:10:22,162
Yes?! What is it?

121
00:10:23,867 --> 00:10:26,859
You won't die
if you give up being a Shinobi.

122
00:10:31,408 --> 00:10:34,844
Why are you so fixated
on being a Shinobi?

123
00:10:38,648 --> 00:10:44,780
My everything is proving that
even I can become a fine Ninja...

124
00:10:47,290 --> 00:10:51,249
You might die. Even if you succeed...

125
00:10:52,228 --> 00:10:53,160
Even so...

126
00:10:54,164 --> 00:10:55,153
<i>I promise you!</i>

127
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:58,461
That's my dream, so...

128
00:11:02,372 --> 00:11:05,136
<i>Why...do you snap this much</i>
<i>at the mention of Hokage's name?</i>

129
00:11:06,843 --> 00:11:09,073
<i>Unlike you...</i>

130
00:11:09,279 --> 00:11:12,339
<i>I will be the heir to the name</i>
<i>of Hokage, no matter what!</i>

131
00:11:13,016 --> 00:11:16,144
<i>Because, Hokage is my dream!</i>

132
00:11:18,822 --> 00:11:22,189
<i>In this village, promising children</i>
<i>are being brought up.</i>

133
00:11:25,662 --> 00:11:30,031
<i>Sarutobi Sensei... Sure enough,</i>
<i>you were a wonderful Hokage.</i>

134
00:11:32,235 --> 00:11:34,726
The surgery is in the afternoon.
Get ready!

135
00:11:36,039 --> 00:11:38,473
Let's go, Lee! Are you prepared?!

136
00:11:38,641 --> 00:11:39,437
Yes!

137
00:11:46,683 --> 00:11:49,880
I got some apples...
You like them, right?

138
00:11:50,587 --> 00:11:52,179
Here, doesn't it look good?

139
00:11:55,124 --> 00:11:57,820
Huh...? I wonder where I put the knife...

140
00:11:58,761 --> 00:12:00,524
It's right in front of you, believe it.

141
00:12:01,130 --> 00:12:05,499
It's so lame, you getting all scatterbrained
just because you're in front of Sasuke.

142
00:12:05,568 --> 00:12:06,830
I'd rather hear lame
from anyone but you...

143
00:12:06,903 --> 00:12:07,835
<i>Naruto...</i>

144
00:12:08,137 --> 00:12:10,867
<i>U zu ma ki!</i>

145
00:12:10,940 --> 00:12:13,374
<i>Naruto 2K Barrage!</i>

146
00:12:17,680 --> 00:12:19,875
Knock it off already!

147
00:12:20,149 --> 00:12:21,639
<i>Summoning Jutsu!</i>

148
00:12:22,552 --> 00:12:26,613
<i>I will...protect Sakura!</i>

149
00:12:27,657 --> 00:12:29,352
I-I give up, believe it...

150
00:12:30,260 --> 00:12:32,091
<i>Sasuke... Thank you.</i>

151
00:12:33,062 --> 00:12:36,395
<i>You rescued me from</i>
<i>the Sand Ninja, right?</i>

152
00:12:36,733 --> 00:12:37,461
<i>No...</i>

153
00:12:38,668 --> 00:12:41,728
<i>The person who rescued you...</i>
<i>was Naruto.</i>

154
00:13:00,790 --> 00:13:03,054
<i>You are weak.</i>

155
00:13:07,697 --> 00:13:09,255
<i>Why are you weak...?</i>

156
00:13:09,432 --> 00:13:11,332
<i>It's because you don't have enough...</i>

157
00:13:12,635 --> 00:13:13,932
<i>...hate.</i>

158
00:13:15,805 --> 00:13:17,295
Good. I peeled it nicely.

159
00:13:17,607 --> 00:13:19,802
I'll cut it to make it easy to eat, and...

160
00:13:21,044 --> 00:13:22,671
Here, Sasuke.

161
00:13:26,215 --> 00:13:27,807
Ow! What happened?

162
00:13:28,318 --> 00:13:29,785
S-Sasuke?

163
00:13:29,886 --> 00:13:31,513
Huh? What's going on?

164
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:38,850
Wh-What?

165
00:13:39,529 --> 00:13:41,690
Y-You don't have to glare
at me like that.

166
00:13:46,169 --> 00:13:47,500
Hey, Naruto...

167
00:13:48,204 --> 00:13:49,262
Wh-What is it?

168
00:13:49,672 --> 00:13:52,140
Fight me... Right now!

169
00:13:53,576 --> 00:13:57,569
What?! Here you are,
just treated by Old Lady Tsunade.

170
00:13:57,914 --> 00:13:59,074
What're you saying?

171
00:13:59,282 --> 00:14:00,681
Just fight!

172
00:14:04,153 --> 00:14:05,120
Sasuke...

173
00:14:05,622 --> 00:14:07,385
You think you saved me?

174
00:14:08,124 --> 00:14:10,058
I don't care if she's the Fifth Hokage
or whatever, but...

175
00:14:10,126 --> 00:14:11,650
she should've just minded
her own business!

176
00:14:12,295 --> 00:14:13,023
What?!

177
00:14:16,199 --> 00:14:18,360
You said you wanted to fight me, right?

178
00:14:18,868 --> 00:14:20,802
I'm saying let's do it now!

179
00:14:21,771 --> 00:14:23,864
Or have you chickened out?

180
00:14:25,675 --> 00:14:29,202
S-Sasuke. Hey...
What's going on?!

181
00:14:29,579 --> 00:14:31,479
Naruto, you say something too!

182
00:14:32,115 --> 00:14:33,275
What's this all of a sudden?

183
00:14:36,252 --> 00:14:37,913
This is perfect, believe it!

184
00:14:38,321 --> 00:14:41,017
I was just thinking
I wanted to fight you!

185
00:14:41,424 --> 00:14:44,325
S-Stop it, the both of you... Okay?

186
00:14:47,363 --> 00:14:48,261
Come with me!

187
00:15:38,781 --> 00:15:42,774
<i>What's...this feeling?</i>
<i>My lower belly feels tight...</i>

188
00:15:43,152 --> 00:15:45,814
<i>I want to fight you, too.</i>

189
00:15:46,956 --> 00:15:49,550
<i>And... I feel a thrill.</i>

190
00:15:55,031 --> 00:15:56,225
What's so funny?

191
00:15:56,332 --> 00:15:59,665
Nothing's funny, believe it!
I'm happy!

192
00:16:00,503 --> 00:16:04,166
When I think
I can finally beat you here!

193
00:16:06,676 --> 00:16:14,139
<i>Abducting Naruto is the No. 1 priority</i>
<i>of our organization, Akatsuki.</i>

194
00:16:15,051 --> 00:16:17,884
What did you say?
Don't talk foolish, you failure!

195
00:16:18,554 --> 00:16:21,819
I'm not going to be
a failure forever!

196
00:16:25,194 --> 00:16:28,391
<i>Right now,</i>
<i>I have no interest in you...</i>

197
00:16:32,769 --> 00:16:37,229
You... A loser like you better
not act all high and mighty!

198
00:16:37,473 --> 00:16:40,965
Hah! It's unlike you to lose
your cool and raise a fuss.

199
00:16:41,043 --> 00:16:42,271
So uncharacteristic.

200
00:16:42,879 --> 00:16:47,248
It couldn't be that you picked a fight
and then got scared, could it, Sasuke?

201
00:16:47,717 --> 00:16:48,911
Just bring it, now!

202
00:16:49,051 --> 00:16:52,248
Put on your headband before that!
I'll wait.

203
00:16:52,455 --> 00:16:54,446
I don't need such a thing...

204
00:16:54,824 --> 00:16:56,189
Just do it!

205
00:16:58,494 --> 00:17:03,454
You wouldn't even be able...
to put one knick on my forehead!

206
00:17:04,233 --> 00:17:05,063
You're wrong!

207
00:17:05,635 --> 00:17:10,095
I'm saying this is a testament to fighting
on equal terms as a Leaf Shinobi!

208
00:17:12,241 --> 00:17:14,402
And I'm saying stuff like that
is acting high and mighty!

209
00:17:14,911 --> 00:17:17,038
Do you think that we're equal?!

210
00:17:17,246 --> 00:17:22,616
Yeah, I do! I've never once
thought that I'm inferior to you!

211
00:17:23,119 --> 00:17:24,814
You're an eyesore!

212
00:17:25,288 --> 00:17:29,725
That's because you remain weak!
Little Sasuke!

213
00:17:30,226 --> 00:17:31,716
Naruto!

214
00:17:32,028 --> 00:17:33,586
Sasuke!

215
00:18:21,077 --> 00:18:22,942
Don't be getting carried away!

216
00:18:38,794 --> 00:18:39,761
<i>Naruto...</i>

217
00:18:44,533 --> 00:18:46,558
Enough already, believe it!

218
00:19:06,756 --> 00:19:08,951
Multi Shadow Clone Jutsu!

219
00:19:42,858 --> 00:19:45,418
U zu ma ki!

220
00:19:54,503 --> 00:19:56,232
Naruto Barrage!

221
00:20:01,677 --> 00:20:02,609
<i>The Tiger Seal!</i>

222
00:20:03,813 --> 00:20:06,247
Fire Style! Fire Ball Jutsu!

223
00:20:16,525 --> 00:20:17,890
N-Naruto!

224
00:20:30,072 --> 00:20:32,267
<i>Wh-What is that Jutsu?!</i>

225
00:20:37,780 --> 00:20:38,576
Damn it!

226
00:20:41,550 --> 00:20:42,574
Chidori: One Thousand Birds!

227
00:20:45,154 --> 00:20:46,553
S-Stop...

228
00:20:46,989 --> 00:20:48,456
I'll win no matter what!

229
00:20:48,624 --> 00:20:50,524
Don't flatter yourself!

230
00:20:51,260 --> 00:20:53,091
Stop it, both of you...

231
00:20:57,166 --> 00:20:58,190
Stop it!

232
00:21:13,516 --> 00:21:20,615
<i>Once in a long while, once in a while</i>

233
00:21:20,756 --> 00:21:26,285
<i>The remnants of a person</i>
<i>broken by dreams</i>

234
00:21:26,462 --> 00:21:31,525
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

235
00:21:34,837 --> 00:21:41,834
<i>Clinging to the Divine,</i>
<i>clinging to Buddha</i>

236
00:21:41,911 --> 00:21:47,440
<i>The remnants of a person crying</i>

237
00:21:47,850 --> 00:21:51,411
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

238
00:21:53,089 --> 00:21:56,149
<i>Rendezvous with a happy dance circle</i>

239
00:21:56,225 --> 00:22:00,025
<i>This is my victory pose, round and around</i>
<i>(round around)</i>

240
00:22:00,362 --> 00:22:03,297
<i>Shake shake shake</i>
<i>Let's look</i>

241
00:22:03,365 --> 00:22:07,495
